Description: Hello Team,

As the title says, DPI is enabled in any case. In globals, computer or even in user, but cannot be enabled in groups. Let me know if you have anything to test or availability for tuesday or wednesday after 10h BRT.

Best regards,
What We've Learned Updated: DPI can be enabled in Device Control -> Global, computer or even in user, but cannot be enabled in groups.
Next Steps Updated: remote session on 15th January
